[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    41[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe Honest Take and the Why This Isn't Production-Ready section together are publication-ready voice; the "Healthcare has a specific structural problem" reframe and the Detection Pattern Catalog and the Statistical-and-ML-Methods layered-architecture posture are the recipe's biggest pedagogical contributions. The MEDIUM-finding cluster is an evenly distributed mix of architectural-completeness gaps (A1 idempotency, A2 DLQs, A3 multi-source-fusion-as-headline-value-add architecturally surfaced, A4 reference-data versioning propagation, A5 suppression-rule schema and expiry-and-review workflow, A6 case-detail-PHI-store separation enforcement) and PHI/governance backstops (S1 cluster payload PHI minimization, S2 subgroup governance). These are the right next-pass priorities; with them addressed, Recipe 3.10 sits at the same publication-ready quality bar as Recipes 3.1-3.9, closing Chapter 3 at the chapter's quality bar.[K
