[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    180[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mPer-publication suppression-aggregation layer.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Each publication path has its own suppression-threshold policy (CDC NSSP aggregates at MMWR-week and county level, public dashboards typically suppress below a small-cell threshold, cross-jurisdictional notifications follow per-receiving-jurisdiction policies, press packages are reviewed by the communications team). The architectural primitive is a publication-layer service that takes a cluster, looks up the publication-target's suppression policy, applies geographic-aggregation-up-the-hierarchy until cell counts meet the threshold, and emits the per-publication-target view.[K
