[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    195[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe nine-stage pipeline (streaming ingest and normalization, syndrome classification, geographic and demographic stratification, aggregation, baseline computation, detector bank, auxiliary-source detectors and multi-source fusion, cluster building, outcome and feedback capture) is the architecturally correct factoring for a public-health-surveillance system. The decision to drive the pipeline with two cadences (streaming per-encounter ingest and classification with sub-30-minute end-to-end latency, and daily-cadence batch computation for baselines and SaTScan) matches the operational reality the prose describes and the public-health-program operating tempo.[K
