[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    197[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe layered-detector architecture (control charts, regression-based methods, spatial scan statistics, spatiotemporal scan, cross-syndrome correlation, auxiliary-source detectors, multi-source fusion) is the architectural discipline that distinguishes operationally-tunable systems from black-box deployments. The closing "reasonable layered architecture" recommendation is operations-engineer voice on the most consequential program-design decision.[K
