[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    305[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThe Step 7 pseudocode does name the fusion mechanic but doesn't architecturally surface the cross-source geographic resolution discipline. Clinical signals operate at census-tract / ZCTA / county granularity; wastewater signals operate at sewershed granularity (which is operationally defined and cuts across administrative boundaries); pharmacy signals operate at retail-pharmacy-catchment granularity; school-absenteeism signals operate at school-district granularity. The pseudocode's [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcandidate_geo_window[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m and [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mmax_score_for[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m mechanic implies that signals across source types fuse cleanly, but the architectural primitive that resolves cross-source geographic relationships (a tract-to-sewershed-to-school-district crosswalk that lets a clinical-tract candidate pull the wastewater-sewershed signal and the school-district-absenteeism signal that cover the same population) is not surfaced in the pseudocode.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    306[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    307[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThe code review's Finding 3 documents this at the Python-companion level: in the Python implementation, [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mmax_score_for[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m matches by direct [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mgeo_id[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m string equality, which means a clinical-tract candidate with [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mgeo_id="36055-001100"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m looks for wastewater signals with [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140msewershed="36055-001100"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (which doesn't exist) and absenteeism signals with [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mdistrict="36055-001100"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (which also doesn't exist); the concordance bonus structurally cannot fire. This expert-review finding is the broader architectural pattern: even if the Python is fixed via a tract-to-sewershed-to-district crosswalk, the recipe-level architecture should make the cross-source geographic resolution a first-class component of the pipeline, with explicit framing about how the crosswalk is maintained, how it relates to the geography hierarchy in Aurora PostGIS, how it handles boundary changes (sewershed reroutes, school-district redistricting), and how the fusion layer reasons about partial coverage (a tract whose population partially feeds a sewershed and partially another).[K
