[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    499[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe opening Tuesday-pediatrician-in-late-October vignette is publication-ready voice. Three kids from the same elementary school, the chart notes that say "viral syndrome, probably the flu that's going around," the four more kids by Friday, the morning huddle's "are we seeing anything weird?", the school nurse's call about twenty-two percent absenteeism, the regional pediatric hospital's six admissions a day, the state lab's eventual sequencing identifying a novel respiratory variant, and the realization that the first case was probably ten or twelve days earlier than anyone realized is the densest public-health-surveillance framing in any cookbook recipe and is the closest the cookbook has come to operational reality of how outbreak detection actually works in most of the country. The pivot to the system reframe ("a continuously running pipeline that ingests clinical encounters, lab results, syndromic indicators, pharmacy data, school absenteeism, wastewater pathogen concentrations, and wearable-device aggregate signals") is the system reframe most first-time builders need to see.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    500[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    501[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe "Healthcare has a specific structural problem that makes this hard" framing is the recipe's biggest pedagogical contribution. The "the baseline isn't a single distribution; it's a pile of overlapping seasonal-trend-residual decompositions" framing is exactly the design lesson that distinguishes mature surveillance programs from generic anomaly-detection deployments.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    502[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    503[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe thirteen-paragraph "the reason this problem lands at the complex end of the chapter" subsection is the densest treatment of public-health-surveillance complexity anywhere in the cookbook. The signal-to-noise framing ("three excess cases against a background of two thousand routine ones") is operationally accurate.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    504[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    505[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Vocabulary You Need subsection is unusually substantive on the public-health-specific terminology. Naming the canonical tooling explicitly (NSSP, BioSense, ESSENCE, NEDSS, NORS, NHSN, MMWR, NWSS, PulseNet) gives the reader the integration landscape rather than abstract framing.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    506[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    507[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Detection Pattern Catalog is the most comprehensive enumeration of public-health-surveillance detection categories in any cookbook recipe, with sixteen named patterns including total-count aberration, spatial cluster, spatiotemporal cluster, demographic-stratified aberration, cross-syndrome correlation, lab-positive cluster, antibiogram drift, HAI cluster, surveillance for known pathogens of concern, sentinel-event detection, genomic cluster, wastewater surge, wearable-aggregate signal, cross-jurisdictional cluster, sub-baseline drop.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    508[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    509[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Statistical and ML Methods subsection is a layered architecture posture done right.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    510[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    511[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Geography-Time-Demographics-The-Hard-Choices subsection is the cleanest treatment of aggregation-choice tradeoffs in the chapter. The "the right answer is 'both, in parallel, with multiple-comparison handling'" framing is the operationally-correct discipline.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    512[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    513[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Workflow-Integration-Is-Again-The-Actual-Product subsection lands the same lesson as Recipes 3.6, 3.7, 3.8, and 3.9 with surveillance-specific factoring (the press-conference-readiness framing, the cross-jurisdictional automatic routing, the public-communication-package generation).[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    514[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    515[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Honest Take is publication-ready voice. The fifteen lessons are the right teaching priorities. Particular highlights: "the signal-to-noise ratio is genuinely brutal in a way that's hard to internalize until you see it," "Multi-source fusion is the biggest leverage point I've seen in the last decade," "Wastewater surveillance changed the field. I was skeptical at first; processing sewage to detect viruses sounded more like a research curiosity than an operational signal. The COVID-19 pandemic proved otherwise," "The biggest disappointment in the field, in my view, has been the slow rollout of eCR," "The biggest mistake I see: programs that get over-excited about advanced analytics and skimp on the basics," and the closing "people matter most, even when they're invisible" framing.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    516[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    517[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe "people matter most, even when they're invisible" closing (the clinicians who first see the unusual cases, the school nurses who notice the absences, the lab technicians who see the unusual culture results, the patients who get sick and get better, or who don't, the surveillance system's purpose to compress the time between the first case and the response) is the kind of moral-clarity framing that distinguishes the cookbook from documentation.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    518[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    519[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe Variations and Extensions section covers nineteen adjacent patterns at substantive depth. The "ESSENCE/NSSP/BioSense integration rather than replacement" framing is the operationally-honest framing for the build-vs-buy decision and matches the framing in The Honest Take.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    520[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    521[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mStyle hygiene is exceptionally clean: zero em dashes (verified directly with U+2014 character check; zero matches), zero en dashes (U+2013 verified), no marketing language, no documentation-voice. The 70/30 vendor balance is preserved cleanly. HTML-comment TODO discipline is correct (thirteen TODOs total, all forward-placeholder, no bracket-style visible TODOs).[K
