[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    643[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe combined picture from the code review's three WARNINGs and this expert review's seven MEDIUM findings is that Recipe 3.10 has the prose-vs-pseudocode-vs-Python asymmetry pattern characteristic of the Recipe 3.7 through 3.9 quality bar. The prose is the strongest in the chapter on multi-source fusion as the headline value-add, suppression-rule lifecycle management, case-detail PHI store separation, suppressed-cell rules at the publication boundary, and surveillance equity; the pseudocode does not architecturally enforce these disciplines; and the Python implementation has three distinct silent-failure correctness bugs. The editorial work is to close the prose-vs-pseudocode gap (A3, A5, A6, S8) without losing the prose's operational authority, and to ensure the Python companion's correctness gaps don't propagate into reader implementations.[K
