[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     78[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m3[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mDownstream analytics consumption is not bounded.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m CloudWatch Logs that contain transcripts can be ingested into log-aggregation platforms, sent to third-party SIEMs, replicated to backup accounts, or queried by Insights. Each downstream consumer becomes another PHI-handling surface that the recordings bucket's governance does not cover.[K
