[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    358[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The recipe correctly identifies the DLQ requirement in the production-gaps section but does not architect the DLQ topology. Each fulfillment Lambda (caller-verifier, intent-router, refill-fulfillment, appointment-fulfillment, urgency-escalator) has independent failure modes and independent retry-and-poison-message semantics. The DLQ topology should specify:[K
