[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    414[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m###[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mFinding A7: Single-Point-of-Failure Analysis for Lex and Connect Outage Is Named in Production-Gaps but Underspecified[K
