[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    428[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m4[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFailover-detection and failover-back triggers.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The detection of the upstream service's recovery and the failover-back to the primary path is automated (Connect health checks; Lex health checks) with the on-call engineer notified at each transition.[K
