[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    438[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Same Finding S2 issue replicated for the appointment-fulfillment path. A duplicate appointment confirmation does not have the same clinical-safety consequence as a duplicate refill, but it produces analytics inflation (the containment rate appears higher than reality), state corruption (the patient's appointment status is updated twice), and downstream notification noise (the patient receives two confirmation SMS).[K
